Kyrial says &quot;okay rolling now                                <br>
Kyrial rolls from 1 to 100 and rolls a 97.&quot;<br>
<br>
Note that the &quot;okay rolling now&quot; isn't actually ended... there's lots of spaces to get it to the next line.  This is why there's now **** in front of your rolls.<br>
<br>
b) there was a way in which hackers could pre-seed a roll... they'd set it that out of 1 to 100 it would always roll 97-100 (to not be too suspicious).  I believe this was fixed.<br>
<br>
I am currently not aware of a way to cheat the rolls.<br>
